# Start using dataproc

Used a persistent history server and elastic ephemeral job clusters with spot instances.

Combine OSS & Google Cloud native engines.

![Dataproc](data:image/png;base64,)

## PHS (Persistent History Server) server

启动常驻集群，用来查看日志。日志集中存储在GSC（对象存储）

```shell
./spark.sh histserver
```

## Ephemeral job server

启动一个弹性任务集群，用来跑独立大任务或者组合小任务。使用完自动（闲置时间配置）或者手动关闭

```shell
./spark.sh jobserver
```

## Submit a sample SparkSQL job

```shell
./spark.sh job
```

可提交`SparkSQL`或者`jar`包

## Update scaling policy

```shell
./spark.sh p
```

配置、更改任务集群弹性策略
